        map - the current Map of the game
        bank - the set of cards available to be distributed to the players
        tradeOffer - the current trade offer, if there is one
        players - the current Players in the game, from 2-4
        version - the version of the model - incremented whenever anyone makes a move
        log - all the log messages for the game's progress
